{
  "stem": "3475.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then after we got-- I think it was Breslau, you know, when we got to-- and who was-- who, who was alive-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] where they packed us into open railroad cars.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was in winter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But they were completely open.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And it was snowing on us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we were huddling together, trying to, you know, keep from freezing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they drove us to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then in Buchenwald-- when we arrived at Buchenwald, they sent us to-- there were, like, enormous barracks, huge barracks.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And when you walked in, there was like a huge hangar almost-- size, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And on each side, there were rows of those wooden pallets stacked up maybe six or eight high, you know, like you put merchandise in.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And there was no straw or anything, you know, just on it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they-- we were packed like six to a pallet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So you could only lay on one side.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you could lay a few hours on one side.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then we had to all together shift over to lay on the other side.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Till you got sores on your bones from laying there, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And basically, there was no work there, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was just warehousing us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then-- at one time or another, I don't remember the place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "While we were in Buchenwald, they shipped us to another area of Germany, which was like in a mountainous area-- pardon me-- where they had factories inside mountains, like a dug-- excavate into the side of mountains, where they had the railroad coming in there.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they, they had machine shops.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember I was working on a machine there, on a lathe, making parts.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
